# Make a bed style format for all the junctions in MAJIQ LSVs
getMAJIQjunctions <- function(x,y){
  juncs <- data.frame(x$chr, str_split_fixed(x[[y]],";", Inf), x$strand,stringsAsFactors = FALSE)
# Find out how many junc columns we have now (number of columns minus chr, strand)
  junc_col_number <- ncol(juncs)-2
# Now I want to seperate each junction column into a seperate 'bed' style dataframe, rbind and remove empty rows
  final_juncs <- data.frame(chr=character(),junction=character(),strand=character(),stringsAsFactors = FALSE)
  for (i in 1:junc_col_number){
    hey <- 1+i
    j <- data.frame(juncs[[1]],juncs[[hey]],juncs[[ncol(juncs)]])
    colnames(j) <- c("chr","junction","strand")
    final_juncs <- rbind(j, final_juncs)
  }
# Get rid of empty & duplicated rows
  final_juncs <- unique(final_juncs [!(final_juncs$junction==""), ])
# Split the junction column into start and stop
  final_juncs  <- data.frame(final_juncs[[1]], str_split_fixed(final_juncs[[2]],'-',2),final_juncs[[3]],stringsAsFactors = FALSE)
  return(final_juncs)
}
myo_net_juncs <- getMAJIQjunctions(myogenesis[myogenesis$`Gene ID` %in% mouse_NE_nets_names,],"Junctions coords")
adi_net_juncs <- getMAJIQjunctions(brown_adipogenesis[brown_adipogenesis$`Gene ID` %in% mouse_NE_nets_names,],"Junctions coords")
rat_net_juncs <- getMAJIQjunctions(all_tissue_rat[all_tissue_rat$`Gene ID` %in% rat_ne_nets_names,],"Junction Coords")
mouse_net_juncs <- getMAJIQjunctions(all_tissue_majiq[all_tissue_majiq$temp...1. %in% mouse_NE_nets_names,],"JuncCoords")
# Now mark the unnanotated junctions 
markAnnotated <- function(x,y){
  colnames(x) <- c("chr","start","stop","strand")
  x$strand <- as.character(x$strand)
  x$chr <- as.character(x$chr)
  x$start <- as.integer(x$start)+1
  x$stop <- as.integer(x$stop)-1
  annot <- inner_join(x=x,y=y)
  novel <- anti_join(x=x,y=y)
  annot$novel <- rep(FALSE,nrow(annot))
  novel$novel <- rep(TRUE,nrow(novel))
  juncs <- rbind(annot,novel)
  return(juncs)
}

Novel junctions that are alternatively spliced

myogenesis <- fwrite(myogenesis,file="/homes/s1207699/data/MYOGEN_LSVS")
brown_adipogenesis <- fwrite(brown_adipogenesis, file="/homes/s1207699/data/ADI_LSVS")
label_myo <- fread("/homes/s1207699/data/MYOGEN_LSVS_novel")
label_adi <- fread("/homes/s1207699/data/ADI_LSVS_novel")
mouse_data <- read.csv("/homes/s1207699/data/rna/mouse_merge_lsvs_annot.tsv",sep=",")
rat_merge_data <- read.csv("/homes/s1207699/data/rna/rat_merge_lsvs_annot.tsv",sep=",")
rat_4_data <- read.csv("/homes/s1207699/data/rna/rat_merge_lsvs_annot_4.tsv",sep=",")
rat_5_data <- read.csv("/homes/s1207699/data/rna/rat_merge_lsvs_annot_5.tsv",sep=",")
myo_nov_nets <- label_myo %>%
  filter(UniqueJunction==TRUE & `Gene ID` %in% mouse_NE_nets_names) %>%
  select(`Gene ID`) %>% unique() %>% nrow()
adi_nov_nets <- label_adi %>%
  filter(UniqueJunction==TRUE & `Gene ID` %in% mouse_NE_nets_names) %>%
  select(`Gene ID`) %>% unique() %>% nrow()
mouse_data_nets <- mouse_data %>%
  filter(UniqueJunction==TRUE & temp...1. %in% mouse_NE_nets_names) %>%
  select(temp...1.) %>% unique() %>% nrow()
rat_data_nets <- rat_merge_data %>%
  filter(UniqueJunction==TRUE & Gene.ID %in% rat_ne_nets_names) %>%
  select(Gene.ID) %>% unique() %>% nrow()
rat_4_nets <- rat_4_data %>%
  filter(UniqueJunction==TRUE & Gene.ID %in% rat_ne_nets_names) %>%
  select(Gene.ID) %>% unique() %>% nrow()
rat_5_nets <- rat_5_data %>%
  filter(UniqueJunction==TRUE & Gene.ID %in% rat_ne_nets_names) %>%
  select(Gene.ID) %>% unique() %>% nrow()
novel_net_junctions <- data.frame(c("myogenesis","brown adipogenesis","rat tissue merge","rat tissue GSE4", "rat tissue GSE5"),
                                  c(myo_nov_nets,adi_nov_nets,rat_data_nets,rat_4_nets,rat_5_nets))
